🤍1 year ago.

I can’t imagine being as over the moon, awestruck, or feel as safe with another person. No matter the geographical distance, I always gravitated towards you and leaned in to the joy you brought me. You possess an undeniable charisma that so few carry. I am amazed by you everyday… you made my black & white world full of color💓

Highlight of Year 1 of Marriage: Finally living in the same city/staying up late every night being silly and the spontaneous experiences/trips with my best friend. I love being married to you. annnnnd the best part? We’re just getting started 🥹

Happy 1st Anniversary, JVG🤍
